        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Who shall be.—He (emphatic) shall become a man of rest, opposed to “a man of war,” such as was David (2Samuel 17:8; 1Chronicles 28:3). The phrase is further explained by what follows.",
