      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "It would seem that the original name of Solomon was Jedidiah (2Samuel 12:25), but posterity, looking back with fond regret to the palmy days of his reign, remembered him only as Shelomoh, “The Peaceful.” (See on 1Chronicles 20:5.)",
        "children": [
