      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "who shall be a man of rest, and I will give him rest from all his enemies round about: and so should be at leisure for such a work, and his people enjoy great prosperity and riches, and so be capable of contributing largely and liberally to it: ",
        "children": []
