        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 22:8",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), it is implied that the divine word was given to him as a command. The reason which David gives why the Lord did not allow him to build the temple is not stated in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 17",
        "children": []
      },
